lead_paragraph: Ireland coach Joe Schmidt had said he wanted to try a few things against Australia to prepare for the Six Nations but playing with a third-choice flyhalf at fullback and replacement scrumhalf on the wing were probably not among them.

headline.print_headline: Makeshift Ireland Hand Schmidt One of His 'Proudest Days'
